Invocation Name: music it
des: A quiz about everything ranging from sitcoms, fiction and general knowledge. This is an all in one quiz for friends and family. Topics like Harry Potter, FRIENDS, Climate Change, Two and a Half Men, Music and even Current Affairs are available in this skill. Just enable it and play it with friends and family. It also keeps a live score which will help you know where you stand in these topics.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
